A simple calculator which computes a few operations based on a given input file uisng arrays and pointers.

Design.md - documenation of thoughts and ideas behind solution
num_arrays.h - function declarations 
num_arrays.c - array calculator function implementations
hw2.c - main client file, takes a given input file and computes a few arithmetic operations on the numbers and outputs the results
Makefile - compiles and creates executable
README - this file!
